{"version":"NotebookV1","origId":1083584440950708,"name":"10-4 One Hot Encoding","language":"python","commands":[{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950709,"guid":"7c2c2792-c3b7-4764-960e-affcec12e76a","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":1.0,"command":"\n%md\n# One-Hot Encoding\n\nIn this notebook we will be adding additional features to our model, as well as discuss how to handle categorical features.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"27147a2f-5b23-4c92-851b-24c7b43ccf13"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950710,"guid":"77670448-99df-444f-b2bb-9d384e36f3d3","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":2.0,"command":"filePath = \"/databricks-datasets/learning-spark-v2/sf-airbnb/sf-airbnb-clean.parquet\"\nairbnbDF = spark.read.parquet(filePath)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"3eecccb8-1693-4cc5-bfc0-b9d419721fde"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950711,"guid":"e07a21bf-a2ff-4234-95e5-28fb33b077ad","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":3.0,"command":"%md\n## Train/Test Split\n\nLet's use the same 80/20 split with the same seed as the previous notebook so we can compare our results apples to apples (unless you changed the cluster config!)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"1e6e9350-5158-4b01-b8dc-faddd67ff0c7"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950712,"guid":"f6563a37-7d3e-4b69-badc-c44228b74469","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":4.0,"command":"trainDF, testDF = airbnbDF.randomSplit([.8, .2], seed=42)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"131fd6c7-2e84-4810-9194-603261ebfa79"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950713,"guid":"fe76f444-23be-40bb-9e63-55d0b79f0a24","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":5.0,"command":"%md\n## Option 1: StringIndexer, OneHotEncoder, and VectorAssembler\n\nHere, we are going to One Hot Encode (OHE) our categorical variables. The first approach we are going to use will combine StringIndexer, OneHotEncoder, and VectorAssembler.\n\nFirst we need to use `StringIndexer` to map a string column of labels to an ML column of label indices [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.feature.StringIndexer)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.feature.StringIndexer).\n\nThen, we can apply the `OneHotEncoder` to the output of the StringIndexer [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.feature.OneHotEncoder)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.feature.OneHotEncoder).","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"8b4ecb6f-8255-40cb-9c42-96db2b9210b0"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950714,"guid":"5c6fbf58-19d6-4c76-a49a-3c47bd7c0aa9","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":6.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.feature import OneHotEncoder, StringIndexer\n\ncategoricalCols = [field for (field, dataType) in trainDF.dtypes \n                   if dataType == \"string\"]\nindexOutputCols = [x + \"Index\" for x in categoricalCols]\noheOutputCols = [x + \"OHE\" for x in categoricalCols]\n\nstringIndexer = StringIndexer(inputCols=categoricalCols, \n                              outputCols=indexOutputCols, \n                              handleInvalid=\"skip\")\noheEncoder = OneHotEncoder(inputCols=indexOutputCols, \n                           outputCols=oheOutputCols)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"b06b81fe-2591-4ff9-a132-be2ed6e64973"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950715,"guid":"4d1a0d90-fb57-41a9-9daa-8a2ff462f07b","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":7.0,"command":"%md\nNow we can combine our OHE categorical features with our numeric features.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"70940f32-f42d-4c8b-a638-1ab881aeef12"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950716,"guid":"b60afc6d-2f0c-4023-9a11-3b86bc5f9b3d","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":8.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.feature import VectorAssembler\n\nnumericCols = [field for (field, dataType) in trainDF.dtypes \n               if ((dataType == \"double\") & (field != \"price\"))]\nassemblerInputs = oheOutputCols + numericCols\nvecAssembler = VectorAssembler(inputCols=assemblerInputs, \n                               outputCol=\"features\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"696e4cc9-0242-4653-ab20-d9afb24747c6"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950717,"guid":"063771b6-527e-472c-bcbb-71ae463d5a4f","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":9.0,"command":"%md\n## Option 2: RFormula\nInstead of manually specifying which columns are categorical to the StringIndexer and OneHotEncoder, RFormula can do that automatically for you [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.feature.RFormula)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.feature.RFormula).\n\nWith RFormula, if you have any columns of type String, it treats it as a categorical feature and string indexes & one hot encodes it for us. Otherwise, it leaves as it is. Then it combines all of one-hot encoded features and numeric features into a single vector, called `features`.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"d646025a-4b12-40fd-bc04-54cdfa979c82"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950718,"guid":"92f80174-0ec8-432f-bbc3-e4617a9cead9","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":10.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.feature import RFormula\n\nrFormula = RFormula(formula=\"price ~ .\", featuresCol=\"features\", labelCol=\"price\", handleInvalid=\"skip\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"1063ff1d-118e-4da3-bbbb-7b034edca9a8"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950719,"guid":"24ea0289-4285-4f9d-9b49-afeb3ebea7df","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":11.0,"command":"%md\n## Linear Regression\n\nNow that we have all of our features, let's build a linear regression model.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"4b79f3ee-ef79-4bd9-9895-f2b60ff02439"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950720,"guid":"c8cf57e7-8068-451a-9866-ec74a7065e50","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":12.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.regression import LinearRegression\n\nlr = LinearRegression(labelCol=\"price\", featuresCol=\"features\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"2a2a9d4a-0261-4090-9610-699412411cee"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950721,"guid":"4e192b97-4f78-4a26-bc08-339cbbce67f9","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":13.0,"command":"%md\n## Pipeline\n\nLet's put all these stages in a Pipeline. A `Pipeline` is a way of organizing all of our transformers and estimators [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.Pipeline)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.Pipeline).\n\nVerify you get the same results with Option 1 (StringIndexer, OneHotEncoderEstimator, and VectorAssembler) and Option 2 (RFormula)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"ceebe97f-09dc-48e9-95c8-a6461c879185"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950722,"guid":"74d6316a-7714-4bf7-8b4e-d0852f55809f","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":14.0,"command":"# Option 1: StringIndexer + OHE + VectorAssembler\nfrom pyspark.ml import Pipeline\n\nstages = [stringIndexer, oheEncoder, vecAssembler, lr]\npipeline = Pipeline(stages=stages)\n\npipelineModel = pipeline.fit(trainDF)\npredDF = pipelineModel.transform(testDF)\npredDF.select(\"features\", \"price\", \"prediction\").show(5)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"749a031d-e8b5-4310-9d81-a02ddc41b903"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950723,"guid":"e54bfaf3-8d01-47b9-8303-f875ba08d708","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":15.0,"command":"# Option 2: RFormula\nfrom pyspark.ml import Pipeline\n\npipeline = Pipeline(stages = [rFormula, lr])\n\npipelineModel = pipeline.fit(trainDF)\npredDF = pipelineModel.transform(testDF)\npredDF.select(\"features\", \"price\", \"prediction\").show(5)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"a219887f-b888-407a-ab0d-af555f5f4ce8"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950724,"guid":"45b249e3-0aea-4c2b-be2c-38655c417d70","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":16.0,"command":"%md\n## Evaluate Model: RMSE","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"0aeea7e7-96bc-41d9-a9dd-6647034b939b"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950725,"guid":"893f9c11-6c74-47b7-99a8-0faccbc30f54","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":17.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.evaluation import RegressionEvaluator\n\nregressionEvaluator = RegressionEvaluator(predictionCol=\"prediction\", labelCol=\"price\", metricName=\"rmse\")\n\nrmse = round(regressionEvaluator.evaluate(predDF), 2)\nprint(f\"RMSE is {rmse}\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"c71a0e37-425d-4391-bb1b-627af45473fd"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950726,"guid":"eab85871-9e39-4043-9c2d-499d20c54e09","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":18.0,"command":"%md\n## R2\n\n![](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/r2d2.jpg) How is our R2 doing? ","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"4d0a0acc-4b0d-4bdf-9798-cacbc88e9286"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950727,"guid":"b22c14c4-82e6-4bac-81cd-89de09946de3","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":19.0,"command":"r2 = round(regressionEvaluator.setMetricName(\"r2\").evaluate(predDF), 2)\nprint(f\"R2 is {r2}\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":